description: NovAccess Global Inc., a biopharmaceutical company, develops novel immunotherapies to treat brain tumor patients in the United States. The company specializes in cutting-edge research related to utilizing a patient's immune system to attack the cancer. NovAccess Global Inc. was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Chesterland, Ohio.
ceo: Dr. Dwain K. Morris-Irvin M.P.H., MPH, Ph.D.
